<p><strong>Dir. McInnis：</strong>它出现了？给我个外景镜头。</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:296px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-5866/Tiamat4.jpg" style="width:296px;" alt="Tiamat4.jpg" class="image" />
